Package: arscpp
Type: Package
Title: Implements the Adaptive Rejection Sampler
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Author: Philipp Hunziker
Maintainer: Philipp Hunziker <hunzikp@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a C++ implementation of Wild and Gilks' (1993) Adaptive Rejection Sampler
    for sampling from univariate log-concave densities. Also implements efficient samplers for the 
    Poisson-Log-Normal (PLN) and multivariate PLN posteriors using ARS and a Gibbs sampler.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.16),
    Matrix
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Suggests:
    testthat, mvtnorm
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
